docs.lead_paragraph: Week Ended July 29, 1960 British pound sterling showed a firm undertone in foreign exchange dealings during the past week. Canadian dollar, strong in the fore part of the week, sold off with the approach of the week-end. Volume of business transacted was fairly heavy at times.
